44:21.870 --> 44:25.040
I don't know what
you've been through, Jan,

44:25.040 --> 44:29.753
but the faith that allowed
him to manipulate

44:29.753 --> 44:34.507
your mom and dad
and all of you,

44:34.507 --> 44:37.218
it's the same faith that's
gonna get you through this.

44:43.850 --> 44:45.518
Guess what?

44:45.518 --> 44:48.188
I got your favorite
in the glove compartment.

44:49.314 --> 44:52.108
Here.

44:55.904 --> 44:57.822
I don't like those anymore.

45:00.200 --> 45:03.370
You're very important
to a lot of people, Jan.

45:03.370 --> 45:04.913
Don't forget that.

45:05.997 --> 45:08.416
Well, I wish I wasn't.

45:12.504 --> 45:14.756
When's Jan getting home?

45:15.924 --> 45:17.258
Any minute.

45:53.378 --> 45:54.963
Hi, Janny.

45:56.006 --> 45:58.341
It's so good to have you home.

46:07.600 --> 46:09.853
We got all your favorites.

46:09.853 --> 46:12.647
We even stayed home
from school.

46:12.647 --> 46:14.357
I'll let you all be.

46:14.357 --> 46:15.817
Thank you.

46:21.990 --> 46:25.201
Well, the woman
of destiny returns.

47:16.961 --> 47:18.546
Jan, honey?

47:18.546 --> 47:20.423
Can we come in?

47:39.984 --> 47:42.237
Is there anything
you wanna talk about?

47:44.948 --> 47:46.491
I'm not your daughter.

47:49.411 --> 47:52.330
I never was,
and I never will be.

47:53.665 --> 47:56.710
The sooner you learn
to accept that, the better.

48:01.423 --> 48:08.388
<i>* ♪</i>
